The <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Freedonian</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">government</ENAMEX> had been faking poverty in order to avoid paying <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">U.N.</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">dues</ENAMEX>. And <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC">Freedonian</ENAMEX> clothing <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">manufacturers</ENAMEX> were able to undersell their <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S.</ENAMEX>
