<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Freedonian</ENAMEX> exports say, "Oh well, I guess that's OK, then"? Whom are we
kidding? The demands for protection would not abate because for the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">U.S.</ENAMEX>
