            Now I come
to berry seizures--not to praise them (sorry, I couldn't help myself) but to
point out how different the case is. For <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">consumers</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">berries</ENAMEX>, it does
